Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Dizelmine! I want to go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could take you there too, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. Today, I have an important meeting to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go for a visit some other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's no fun. Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might get sick again if you overexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{You should be taking a break after our long journey.}You should take this time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize this is part of your duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still must applaud you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assign more chaperons to her so that she doesn't go off on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pass on your instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on ya.
