Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that thing from yesterday was all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean about the experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There was that thing with Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the girl who appeared in my cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would never forgive me for seeking asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm sure Asteria will make things work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't joke about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Watabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I will begin preparations right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've received word that shuttles have departed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}both the Le Garite and De Metrio mother ships with their respective kings aboard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this ends without any incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a fist fight breaks out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's better than having them start a galactic war near Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to see you're in good health too, Captain Tadokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More lady troubles I see, by the looks of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Majesty, King of Le Garite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you install this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm here with friends. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here with my subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regal, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the information we have of the two of you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being best friends since your Academy days is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've prepared a quiet location suited for your historical conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my younger sister aboard this vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She and her two friends are engaging in girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? First one to find them can revoke their asylum status?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like becoming the king has given you a better sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're starting this already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asteria, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the quiet place suited for our historic conference, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you put her up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that girl's the type who listens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to hear what the boys have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About our childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But come to think of it, weren't we locked up together like this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when our shuttle reactor went into overload after failing on a subspace trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the year I went to study abroad at your Academy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were both in our first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've just waited for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to your meddling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it took them two more weeks to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Except if I hadn't, the ship would've been completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was alone, I could have saved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they both went to the same school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder they seem to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look that way to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, looks like we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moid?! And... why're you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we'd like to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villagiulio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the middle of a conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that a conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made these special arrangements for those two shy boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you say will change the Chairman's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just watch and see how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wasn't yesterday the first time you witnessed the power of the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you used your sister for an experiment, I hear you were unable to open the Rin-ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought the legend might've scared you and kept you awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like when you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was also scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a scaredy-cat, just like you, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I didn't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that power, I can solve the 1,000-year problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the rumors about you wanting to use the Vox to destroy our planet are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wish to avert the disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, more than anyone, should know the danger of the Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under our research and care,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can expand on Vox Aura's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can avoid further tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Aura's pilot is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... {\i1}special?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's finally revealing his true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really that into Madoka, then I may need to change plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, why don't we just fight over her as warring nations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unregistered aircraft has left the Le Garite mother ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jim?{he's dead}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No response from the Occupation Forces, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're letting it through. Get me through to Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadokoro here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ovid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain, Moid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some pretty bad flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of your pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No complaints if we take care of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be my guest. Go easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pilot sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm any better, but still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That direction! It's headed for Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get a Kamopaccio, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. One Kamopaccio coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Izo! It's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worried about that thing from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what happened on Militia happens on this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,think how many people would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of Le Garite and Villagiulio are in talks to avoid just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano paved the way for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many more of these Sangayaki Lunch Specials do we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ovid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Le Garite production model!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, I think it's coming right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. Gotta get to Kamogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is Le Garite thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose they're here for the conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, they're nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Le Garite pilot! You can hear me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kamogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a designated neutral zone of De Metrio and Le Garite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... I hurt my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your hands off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to speak with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Array!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you recognize me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Lord Dizelmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke your promise and came here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a bad girl, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuriyuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess of De Metrio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Villagiulio's real younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I know that in his heart, he considers you as his little sister, Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about which of you two he loves more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Lan. That's not the problem right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. His real sister, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get it, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Lan, what was Yurikano doing on Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come on the same ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Lady Yurikano several times when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never saw her on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know that we were on board together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother didn't say anything during our trip here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means your younger sister is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking why she was with the Le Garite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rescued her from the Tragedy of Militia Zodia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were busy leading some rogues and calling yourselves Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I feared she wouldn't make it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but {we finally managed to heal her up to this point.}she finally managed to recover as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As her older brother, shouldn't you be happy for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This man is your real older brother, Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't remember a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not even about her being the princess of De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biotelemetry numbers are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her DNA pattern is a perfect match with Lady Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's behaving exactly like when she was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right down to calling herself Yuriyuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to try to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving without Lord Dizelmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've trained her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what about our conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it was our fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think continuing the talks might be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall meet at the Intergalactic Conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse us, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Villagiulio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to let them go like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't talk to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But! But I feel so sorry for Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to apologize for, Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go and see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should act now while it's still fresh in our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was all this commotion part of your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to speak with Miss Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, you appeared in my cockpit, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cockpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind telling me what this is about, Miss Kyouno Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, during the course of our experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she appeared in the cockpit of Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very odd. She was with me the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was definitely Miss Yurikano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yuriyuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall meeting with Miss Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't know you. {lol this was a nice troll}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you grappled and tussled me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! What about before that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also met another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Asteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough. Now's not the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I guess we'll do as she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely that girl. I'm positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she's the real Miss Yurikano,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't she act more unwilling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we need to have a proper talk with her!{realtalk}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Big Brother Giuvi and Lan's brother will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's sneak in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneak in where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, you'll never get a chance to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yurikano is on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will continue negotiations regarding Lady Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to assign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more chaperons to Yurikano, did I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it {\i1}did {\i0}allow us to gather some unexpected information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to return to Le Garite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with, uh... my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse us, coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never been to Tokyo, but outer space just fascinates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been begging Laffy to take me there with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can call me Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki Namie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to let them go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We're in a big hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no excuse for me to manhandle my fishnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a fisherman, they're nearly as dear as life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should know that by now after being in Kamogawa for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Izo, when are you going to ask Sachi out to the movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never made such a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! How tangled can these nets get?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The Le Garite shuttle's taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurikano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! How freakin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success says, "Wow"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just leave it to me", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super amazing. yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"After all, I'm a member of Kiss", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is crazy, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super amazing, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fun?! I feel sorry for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take off those disguises now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Madoka. Miss Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Dizelmine is hellbent on going to war with me.
