Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! This spaceship is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are even sections of it that I'm not familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's where Miss Yurikano is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, she wouldn't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that place is an eel farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spaceship really is huge...
